This software was created for sound and plasma art installation "Zoryas" imagined by Claire Williams and brought to life with the code of  Baptiste de la Gorce in 2019-2020. This installation is a production of Le Fresnoy - Studio National des Arts Contemporains.
This software has been made with the help of : 
- The royal observatory of Beligum thanks to Petra Vanlommel & Christophe Marqué.
- The E- Callisto network setup by Christian Monstein http://e-callisto.org/ giving us access to 24 h sun monitoring the electromagnetic activity of the sun with ... radiotelescopes around the world.

And the precious advice of: 
Jean Phillipe Uzan, cosmologue 
Renée Prange & Philipe Zarka from l'OBSPM of Paris
Sébastien Cabour, sound artist and technical advisor.

