~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Requirements:
Tested on raspian - debian.

Python 3.5
Pip
aplay

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
# creation du repository ---------------------------
hg clone https://login:motdepass@bitbucket.org/guilbut/smartrobot
hg update default -C

# mise à jour du repository ----------------------
hg pull https://login:motdepass@bitbucket.org/guilbut/smartrobot
hg update default -C

$ sudo python3.5 fitDownloader.py
$ sudo python3.5 fitPlayer.py
